lead_paragraph: South Korea's Ha Na Jang enhanced her growing reputation as one of the hottest players on the LPGA Tour by winning the HSBC Women's Champions tournament by four strokes on Sunday.

headline.print_headline: Ha Na Jang Takes LPGA Singapore Title by 4 Strokes
